<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="container about__inner">
    <h2 class="section-heading">About</h2>
    <p>
      I'm a mobile engineer. For six years I was the only frontend developer
      on Guusto's React Native app, which I built from scratch and shipped to
      both stores. My work covered the whole pipeline. I took Figma designs
      and turned them into TypeScript code, handled native integrations and
      client-side push, and did the release work that keeps an app on the
      stores, like cert renewals, store review rejections, and crash triage.
      I'm based in Japan on a spouse visa, so I don't need sponsorship. I'm a
      native English speaker and I'm learning Japanese. I worked fully remote
      for all six years, first from Canada, then Australia, then Japan, with
      the same Vancouver team the whole time. The time gap ran as wide as 16
      hours. In practice I wrote a clear handoff note at the end of my day
      and read Slack at the start of it.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

